/-! ### AP3: Cauchy index theorem target for the unit kernel -/

/-- Cauchy index for the unit kernel around a rectangle:
`Ôê« dz / (z - a) = 2¤Çi` for `a` strictly inside the rectangle.

This is the smallest remaining analytic theorem in the residue-free
