/-! ### BT3: analyticity of remainder closes the contour decomposition -/

/-- **BT3 ÔÇö UNCONDITIONAL ASSEMBLER:** linearity (BS6) + analyticity of the
remainder (BT2) ÔçÆ principal-part contour decomposition.  The remainder
