structure ConcreteSRightClosure (lower : ÔäØ) : Prop where
  closure :
    ÔêÇ T : ÔäØ, lower Ôëñ T ÔåÆ
      (ÔêÇ ╬Á : ÔäØ, 0 < ╬Á ÔåÆ
        Ôêâ U : ÔäØ, RvMGoodHeight U Ôêº lower Ôëñ U Ôêº T Ôëñ U Ôêº U < T + ╬Á Ôêº
          |concreteS U| Ôëñ (1 / 2 : ÔäØ) * Real.log U + 1 / 2) ÔåÆ
      |concreteS T| Ôëñ (1 / 2 : ÔäØ) * Real.log T + 1 / 2

/-! ### CP2: right-sided good-height density above a positive threshold -/

/-- Right-sided refinement of `exists_goodHeight_near_right_ge_lower`:
