/-! ### CP4: final theorem using right closure for the Backlund side -/

/-- **CP4 ÔÇö final theorem with right-sided Backlund closure:** uses the
right-sided closure (CP1) for the Backlund bound side, alongside the
RvM-formula closure (CO2). -/
theorem
    ConcreteSBacklundEstimateFrom140OnGoodHeights.to_concreteS_halfLogPlusHalf_of_rightClosures
    (F : ZetaFunctionalEquationStandardZeroFactsViaTransfer)
