/-! ### CW12: separated analytic Backlund inputs aggregator -/

/-- Separated analytic Backlund inputs: the three sharp analytic
packages (Jensen window, right-side log-derivative, horizontal ╬Â growth)
plus the classical `combine` lemma that assembles them into the good-
