  combine :
    ÔêÇ T : ÔäØ, RvMGoodHeight T ÔåÆ (140 : ÔäØ) Ôëñ T ÔåÆ
      BacklundJensenRectangleEstimate T ÔåÆ
      BacklundRightSideArgumentVariationEstimate T ÔåÆ
      BacklundHorizontalBoundaryEstimate T ÔåÆ
        |concreteS T| Ôëñ (1 / 2 : ÔäØ) * Real.log T + 1 / 2

/-- Bridge: the separated analytic inputs assemble into the classical
inputs structure. -/
noncomputable def BacklundSeparatedAnalyticInputs.toClassicalInputs
