/-- **CW12 ÔÇö FINAL THEOREM from four sharp analytic inputs + LC.**

The headline bound `|concreteS T| Ôëñ (1/2)┬Àlog T + 1/2` (for every
`T ÔëÑ 140`) is reduced to:
- `I.jensen` : Jensen window estimate on the weighted zero count;
- `I.rightSide` : right-side argument-variation / log-derivative bound;
- `I.horizontal` : horizontal ╬Â growth bound;
- `I.combine` : classical Backlund combination lemma;
- `LC` : right local-constancy of the weighted zero count. -/
theorem concreteS_halfLogPlusHalf_of_separatedBacklund_and_countLC
    (I : BacklundSeparatedAnalyticInputs)
    (LC : ZetaWeightedZeroCountRightLocalConstancyInput)
    {T : ÔäØ} (hT : (140 : ÔäØ) Ôëñ T) :
