/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö T-dependent first-zero band dispatcher.**
Four sub-certs Ôƒ╣ full first-zero-band cert at any probe `T Ôêê [2¤Ç, 10]`. -/
theorem firstZeroBand_modelMarginT_of_inputs
    (model : ÔäØ ÔåÆ Ôäé ÔåÆ Ôäé) (errorBound : Ôäé ÔåÆ ÔäØ ÔåÆ ÔäØ)
    (I : FirstZeroBandCertInputsT model errorBound)
