        `╬¥'/╬¥ s = 1/s + 1/(sÔêÆ1) ÔêÆ ┬¢┬Àlog ¤Ç + ┬¢┬À¤ê(s/2) + ╬Â'/╬Â s`;
      ÔÇó integrated paired-Cauchy form via the ┬º13 IBP package once
