/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö Helper 3b: `log(13/(2¤Ç)) ÔëÑ 1/2`.**
Via `Real.add_one_le_exp(-1/2)` Ôƒ╣ `exp(1/2) Ôëñ 2 Ôëñ 13/(2¤Ç)`. -/
lemma log_13_div_2pi_ge_1_2 :
