/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö `slabSimple_12_13_core`.** Clean assembly via the
existing helpers; no unfolding, no log, no denominator clearing. -/
lemma slabSimple_12_13_core
    {x y T : ÔäØ}
    (hx : 0 Ôëñ x) (hT12 : 12 Ôëñ T) (hT13 : T Ôëñ 13)
    (hy : 0 < y) (hreg : 2 * (1 + x + y) Ôëñ T) :
