-- ┬ºCCXVIII. Adaptive bound data + wrapper-kernel ActualDensityTailData
-- =====================================================================
-- Closes the wiring loop: adaptive convergence (┬ºCCXVII) plus the
-- finite-Im identity (┬ºCCXVI) plus real IBP data give an
-- `AdaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData`, which produces the `hbound`
-- field, which feeds `ActualDensityTailData`, which feeds the
-- `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage` via the ┬ºCCXIII model-parametric
-- theorem. Adds:
--
--   AdaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData                ÔÇö adaptive Prop bundle
--   adaptiveComplexDensityTailFamilyPartial_im_tendsto
--   hbound_of_adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData      ÔÇö produces hbound
--   adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData_pairedDeriv    ÔÇö wrapper instantiation
--   actualDensityTailData_of_pairedDerivWrapper    ÔÇö full ActualDensityTailData
--   localXiPackage_of_pairedDerivWrapper           ÔÇö final local package
--
-- After this lands, the only remaining gap in the real-tail direction
