    hbound_of_adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData
      (adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData_of_trueKernelTailData S R error D)

/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage` from
`TrueKernelTailData`.** The final entry point of the true-kernel chain.
Combines a real-IBP family, a model, the xi log-derivative
