/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **CONDITIONAL CAPSTONE ÔÇö `XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget`
from `TrueKernelTailData`.**

Routes the ┬ºCCXXI true-kernel chain through the ┬ºCXL covering family
