/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **CONDITIONAL CAPSTONE (concrete finite-fluctuation
form).** The ┬ºCCXXII bundled capstone instantiated to
`S = finiteFluctuationPrimitive D T0`, with the `R` slot supplied
