/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **CLEAN FRONT DOOR ÔÇö `XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget`
from `XiActualTailDecompositionData`.** Three explicit inputs:

