/-- ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö partials converge to `trueKernelTailOfLogEnvelope`.**
Direct `Classical.choose_spec` of ┬ºCCLIII's existence theorem. -/
theorem trueKernelTailOfLogEnvelope_tendsto
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : ÔäØ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0)
    {C D T : ÔäØ} {z : Ôäé}
