-- =====================================================================
-- ┬ºCCLXII. High residual formula data + master residual front door
-- =====================================================================
-- Per the user's design note: high-region points may not have a valid
-- mid cutoff (e.g. `2(1+|z.re|+z.im) > 140` means no `T Ôêê [10, 140]`
-- exists), so `XiHighResidualTailIdentity` is genuinely independent
-- of the mid-band `XiResidualFormulaData`. This section adds the
-- analogous high wrapper and the master front door composing all
-- residual-flavored xi obligations.
--
-- Adds:
--   XiHighResidualFormulaData                                ÔÇö high Prop wrapper
--   highLocalPackage_of_XiHighResidualFormulaData            ÔÇö high local pkg builder
--   lowLocalPackage_of_residualLowMargin                     ÔÇö low local pkg builder
--   XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_residualPackages         ÔÇö master front door

/-- ­ƒôª **`XiHighResidualFormulaData`** ÔÇö Prop wrapper around
`XiHighResidualTailIdentity`. Same shape as the mid-band
`XiResidualFormulaData`; kept separate because high-region `z` need
