/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö `XiHighResidualTailIdentity` from a complex
Tendsto witness.** If the residual `xiResidualError M z` is the limit
of the true-kernel complex partials over `[T, X]` as `X ÔåÆ Ôê×` for every
high-band `(z, T)`, then the high residual Im identity follows: take
