/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö canonical mid `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage`.**
Bundles the canonical mid residual into a `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage`
