--   zeroDensitySmoothTailModel_neg_im_tendsto_real_integral    ÔÇö real Tendsto bridge

/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö complex Tendsto witness for the honest smooth tail.**
The finite complex partials `smoothDensityTailModelPartial zeroDensityRho Tsmooth X z`
converge to `zeroDensitySmoothTailModel Tsmooth hTsmooth_ge z` as
