/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö `positiveSmoothKernel` is continuous in `u` for `y Ôëá 0`.**
Denominators `(x ┬▒ u)┬▓ + y┬▓ ÔëÑ y┬▓ > 0` are nonvanishing. -/
lemma positiveSmoothKernel_continuous {x y : ÔäØ} (hy : y Ôëá 0) :
    Continuous (fun u : ÔäØ => positiveSmoothKernel x y u) := by
  have hy2 : (0 : ÔäØ) < y ^ 2 := by positivity
  unfold positiveSmoothKernel
  refine continuous_const.mul ?_
  refine Continuous.add ?_ ?_
  ┬À refine continuous_const.div ?_ ?_
    ┬À exact ((continuous_const.sub continuous_id).pow 2).add continuous_const
    ┬À intro u
      have h : (0 : ÔäØ) Ôëñ (x - u) ^ 2 := sq_nonneg _
      linarith
  ┬À refine continuous_const.div ?_ ?_
    ┬À exact ((continuous_const.add continuous_id).pow 2).add continuous_const
    ┬À intro u
      have h : (0 : ÔäØ) Ôëñ (x + u) ^ 2 := sq_nonneg _
      linarith

/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö `positiveSmoothKernel` is interval-integrable.** -/
