/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö `¤ü ┬À K` is interval-integrable on `[a, b] Ôèé (0, Ôê×)`.** -/
lemma zeroDensity_mul_positiveSmoothKernel_intervalIntegrable
    {x y a b : ÔäØ} (ha : 0 < a) (hab : a Ôëñ b) (hy : y Ôëá 0) :
    IntervalIntegrable
