      |(xiResidualError M z).im|
        Ôëñ |lowFirstZeroBoundaryTerm Dzero T0 z.re z.im 11|
          + |lowFirstZeroDerivativeSide Dzero T0 z.re z.im 11 14|

/-- ­ƒôª **`FirstZeroGapForDzero Dzero T0 ╬│`** ÔÇö first-zero-gap identity
for the fluctuation primitive: on `[2¤Ç, ╬│]` the finite fluctuation
