/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö `|S(u)| Ôëñ 1/2` on `[11, 14]`** from `FirstZeroGapForDzero`
at `╬│ = 14` and `abs_smoothZeroCountingN0_le_half_on_first_band_14`. -/
theorem finiteFluctuation_abs_le_half_on_11_14
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : ÔäØ}
    (Hgap : FirstZeroGapForDzero Dzero T0 14)
