-- where `smoothLBConst := (259/3586)┬À(5/29) Ôëê 0.01246`. The factor
-- `5/29` is the uniform LB for the kernel factor (equality at `(0, 4)`);
-- `259/3586` is the rational LB for `¤ü(10)` via Pad├® `log(5/¤Ç) ÔëÑ 74/163`
