* `XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource` ÔÇö Hadamard product / log-derivative source
* `XiZeroContributionSplit` ÔÇö Stieltjes decomposition of the zero sum -/
theorem XiExplicitFormulaPackage_of_hadamardSource_and_zeroSplit
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : ÔäØ}
    {M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition}
    (Hsrc : XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource)
    (Hsplit : XiZeroContributionSplit Dzero T0 M Hsrc.zeroContribution) :
    XiExplicitFormulaPackage Dzero T0 M := by
  refine Ôƒ¿?tail, ?lowÔƒ®
  ┬À refine Ôƒ¿?_Ôƒ®
    intro z T hy hregime
    obtain Ôƒ¿L, hL, hZÔƒ® := Hsplit.high_tail_split hy hregime
    refine Ôƒ¿L, hL, ?_Ôƒ®
