    filter_upwards [Filter.eventually_ge_atTop (canonicalAdaptiveT z)] with u hu
    exact hTuring h10 h140 hy hregime hu
  obtain Ôƒ¿L, hLÔƒ® :=
    trueKernelComplexTail_converges_at_of_logEnvelope
      Dzero T0 hT0_pos hT0leT hTpos hy hEnv
  exact Ôƒ¿L, Ôƒ¿hLÔƒ®Ôƒ®

/-- ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ­ƒîƒ **PROVED ÔÇö high convergence at any `T ÔëÑ 140` from `hHighLog`.**
