/-- Ô¡É **PROVED ÔÇö off ╬ô-poles implies the Deligne ╬ô-factor is nonzero.** -/
theorem GammaReal_ne_zero_of_half_not_gammaPole
    {s : Ôäé} (hsPole : s / 2 Ôêë gammaPoleSet) :
